{"tid":335055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學界警告：蔡若蓮上任　教育再赤化","createTime":"2017-07-25T09:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T17:32:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aabb3e393de917dc9eeb6260af8c06239f0bba72","tid":335055,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:32:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20100863&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20100863%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170725&d=k6tLU5ag40v2dGNDhWlZkuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=7a393ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20100863%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170725&h=d4c3d09b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20100863&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170725</a><br />\n<br />\n學界警告：蔡若蓮上任　教育再赤化<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n多個學界團體昨在記招展示蔡若蓮戴紅領巾照。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】外界盛傳「深紅底」的教聯會副主席蔡若蓮將出任教育局副局長，惹來反彈。學聯和港語學等學界團體，斥蔡一直力推「中普融合」及國民教育，警告若蔡上任，香港教育將進一步赤化，並要求與蔡公開對話。<br />\n港語學召集人陳樂行指，蔡若蓮約在2006至2013年於教育局任職高級課程發展主任。教育局網頁2014年初曾爆出「廣東話不是法定語言的中國方言」風波，翻查後發現網站2013年8月已有相關紀錄。而蔡當時正是語文支援組的負責人，可見蔡連擔任主任都不稱職，無法勝任副局長一職，「唔止係針對佢嘅背景，佢係真係冇料」。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒：任命將終結蜜月期<br />\n<br />\n陳又指，多份由蔡負責的教育局文件顯示，蔡一直力推中普融合和普教中，如2012年的「語文教學支援組支援範圍」文件，詳細寫明要以普教中、「優化」普通話學習等。但蔡離職後，有關文件的「普教中」字眼隨即消失，相信如蔡重返教育局，普教中定必死灰復燃。<br />\n在2012年牽頭反國教的香港眾志黃之鋒說，教聯會是國教推手，指「中國共產黨是進步、無私和團結」的《中國模式》教材，正是教聯會轄下的國民教育服務中心獲得教育局資助後出版，質疑作為教聯會副主席的蔡上任副局會私相授受，以公帑撥款出版洗腦教材，重推國教。<br />\n黃指，去年立法會選舉已明顯知道蔡是「西環契女」，現時更以空降姿態進入教育局，「乜叫西環治港？林鄭嘅任命就好完整體現出嚟」。如特首林鄭月娥仍堅持任命蔡，林鄭的蜜月期會立即終結。他指明天會到教聯會，要求與蔡若蓮公開對話。<br />\n■記者李詠希<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n蔡若蓮"},{"pid":"1b75adbb3ebb2ac03bc5dc0cdfc7f94da24a0642","tid":335055,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170725/large/25la5p12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170725%2Flarge%2F25la5p12.jpg&h=6d46860b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多個學界團體昨在記招展示蔡若蓮戴紅領巾照。"},{"pid":"b899279a715a1a0df6c9b9ad416bfedd85d638fd","tid":335055,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"俾一個自己教育界都唔投嘅人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466bf412db48f4dd3d199a92115cc99749318567","tid":335055,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3ed37db9c49c4723970d9214c2f5cc2f1693c2","tid":335055,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa42c68b1889cc825b4d681b50642ce84deaace1","tid":335055,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33d1435cbdb9e073b835f1df9114c0a00b245bf","tid":335055,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"日日都赤化緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0db3dbc965586ad6513a836b33c54a27c9312b","tid":335055,"uid":108282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:21:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/蔡若蓮\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%A5%E8%93%AE&d=k6tLU5ag40v2dGNDhWlZkuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=743fffb2\" data-au